channel.title: I need help with my server!
channel.description: well, i don't know what my problem is, but i've gotten my server to the point by updating it where there's nothing more to do before i bring it online. so i got my no-ip [alanscape.no-ip.info] and i [owner] log in as localhost, but my friends when i check the box and click run server aren't able to log in, and i can't manage my server into the server list, because it tells me it's not online, but i can still log in.. port fowarding doesn't work because when i got to my default gateway it tells me that i need a password & user, so i looked up my default on portfoward.com and my default didn't work.. so i'm having trouble bringing my server online. can anyone help me? it'll be GREATLY appriciated.

item.title: I need help with my server!
item.dc:creator: @Alan Alan
item.description:
@Alan wrote:

well, i don’t know what my problem is, but i’ve gotten my server to the point by updating it where there’s nothing more to do before i bring it online. so i got my no-ip [alanscape.no-ip.info] and i [owner] log in as localhost, but my friends when i check the box and click run server aren’t able to log in, and i can’t manage my server into the server list, because it tells me it’s not online, but i can still log in… port fowarding doesn’t work because when i got to my default gateway it tells me that i need a password & user, so i looked up my default on portfoward.com and my default didn’t work… so i’m having trouble bringing my server online. can anyone help me? it’ll be GREATLY appriciated.
